              <entry>
                <string>content</string>
                <string>Hello normal line not in context.

This sentence contains an annotated part and is followed with random words that are not annotated.

This is another normal line not in context.

(% data-table-width="760" data-layout="default" %)
|=(((
**in th before annotated after in th**
)))|=(((
**annotated in th**
)))
|(((
in td before annotated after in td
)))|(((
annotated in td
)))
|(((
this should never be in selection context
)))|(((
this neither
)))

Random sentence without annotation

= {{id name="Inlinecommentcontext-Randomtitlewithannotatedpartandwordsafter"/}}Random title with annotated part and words after =

This is a random sentence that should not be in context

== {{id name="Inlinecommentcontext-Completelyannotatedtitle"/}}Completely annotated title ==

(% start="1" %)
1. This item is not annotated
1. This item is partly annotated and has words after
1. This item is completely annotated
1. This item is not annotated neither

This is a random sentence that should not be in context

>This is an annotated citation

This is a random sentence that should not be in context

>This is a partly annotated citation

This is a random sentence that should not be in context

>This is a paragraph in a citationThis paragraph is annotatedThis paragraph is not annotated

In this sentence, there are two annotations that are nested and some words after.</string>
              </entry>
              <entry>
